org.jlab.mya

Class ExtraInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jlab.mya.ExtraInfo

  • public final class ExtraInfo
extends Object
    Provides additional information about an EPICS PV, which unlike standard Metadata, is versioned (may change over time).

    Extra info types include:

    • "enum_strings"
    • "notes"
